h the response in Marias's characters is more rationalized, analyzed over and over, while in The Lowland it leaves the characters partially stunted, emotionally paralyzed and sort of vacant. Of course, the individual reactions vary, but there's this common empty room in their hearts that refuses to be filled. Lahiri drives this point home painfully and beautifully through actual vacated spaces: balconies, home offices, beds, chairs, etc. where the absent linger in spirit, forever haunting the ones who stayed. This is a powerful emotional read, and obviously a very sad one, though I could discern mostly hope in the final pages.\u003cbr /\u003eIf you're looking for a grand, sweeping, but intimate novel that will find a spot in your heart and refuse to let go, don't miss this one.","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2079375?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"asia","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2079375?shelf=asia"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"n-america","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2079375?shelf=n-america"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"literary","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/2079375?shelf=literary"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/672619135"},"likeCount":92,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":13,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.V8EQj5lKPjM3C-DINVZEoA":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.V8EQj5lKPjM3C-DINVZEoA","__typename":"Book"},"User:100264072":{"id":100264072,"__typename":"User","legacyId":100264072,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1621672092i/100264072._UX200_CR0,33,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":527,"viewableName":"Swaroop","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webU